pan class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chabadlibrary.org/catalog/index1.php?frame=main&amp;catalog=ecatalog&amp;mode=details&amp;volno=4231&amp;limit=0&amp;field=TITLE&amp;search=COMPLETE+&amp;search_mode=simple\">ראו פרטי החוברת בקטלוג ספריית ליובאוויטש</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">כך לדוגמה במהדורות שהודפסו בשנים תשל\"ג, תשל\"ה, ו<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chabadlibrary.org/catalog/index1.php?frame=main&amp;catalog=ecatalog&amp;mode=details&amp;volno=4249&amp;limit=0&amp;field=TITLE&amp;search=COMPLETE+&amp;search_mode=simple\">תשד\"מ (מהדורה שנים עשר)</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413030217\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.071 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.485 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 169/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2673/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 63/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2564/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.030/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5750784/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  390.634      1 -total\n 78.97%  308.497      4 תבנית:הערה\n 14.67%   57.300      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  5.74%   22.425      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים/מרחב_שם\n  4.19%   16.387      1 תבנית:ספריית_המל&quot;ח\n  2.37%    9.245      2 תבנית:שורה_אחת\n  1.98%    7.744      1 תבנית:בית_חבד\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:74236-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413030217 and revision id 813625. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"
